&lt;p>title: Skew Braces, the YBE, and some results in the classification of solutions
event: Algebra seminar
event_url: &lt;a href="https://mathsseminars.leeds.ac.uk/seminars/2025-05-13-silvia-properzi-vrije-universiteit-brussel/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://mathsseminars.leeds.ac.uk/seminars/2025-05-13-silvia-properzi-vrije-universiteit-brussel/&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
